      "text": "To Reddetu Swehtkus\nbuhs jums arridsan turreht / to\nPirmaju Swehtkus tahs Kwee-\nchu Ptauschanas / un tahs Sa-\nrafschanas Swehtkus / kad\nSad6 pa Gallam irr.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Trihsreifsi Gadsfahrtâ\nibs wiſſemi/ kas juhsu Starpâ\nihriftis irr/ rahditees preefsch\nKunga KUNGA / Israëta\newa.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Rad es tohs Paganus ts-\nofchu tavâ Preekfchâ / un is-\nttischu tawas Rohbeschäs /\nne eefahrohs neveens tawu\nmmi/ kamehr tu eefi rahdi-\nees preefsch ta KUNGA ta-\nDeewa trihsreifsi Gads\ntâ.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tew ne buhs manna Up-\nAffini ar faraudsetahn\nsehm uppureht/ ir to Passa-\nehtku Uppuram ne buhs zaur\nti lihds Rihtam palikt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 26,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "TohsPirmajus no tawas\nmes pirmajeem Augfeem/\ntew nest eefsch ta KUNGA\nDeewa Namna / tew ne\nto Ahsiti wahriht/ kas wehl\nwas Mahtes Peena.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 27,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tas KUNGS fazzija\nohsu: Raksti schohs Wahr-\njo pehz fcheem Wahrdeem\nes ar tew / un ar Israëlu\nu Derribu darrijs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 28,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch bija tur ar to\nGu tfchetrddefmits Deenas/\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 29,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tfchetrddefmits Naktis/ winſch\nne ehde Maist / un ne dsehre Uh-\ndeni/ un winſch rakstija us teem\nGaldixeem tahs Derribas Wahr-\ndus/ tohs defmitis Wahrdus.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 30,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un kad Mohsus no ta\nKalna Sinâi nogahje/tad bija tee\ndiwi Leezibas Galdixi Mohsus\nRohkâ/ kad tas no ta Kalna no-\nguhje/tad ne finnaja Mohsus/ ka\nwinna Waiga Ahda spihdeja /\nkad winſch ar to runnaja.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 31,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kad nu Aärons un wiſſi\nIsraëta Behrni Mohsu usluh-\nkoja/redsi/ tad spihdeja winna\nWaiga Ahda / tapehz bihjajahs\ntee pee winna tuwn nahkt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 32,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad fanze tohs Mohsus/\nun pee winna atgreesahs Aärons\nun wiſſi Draudsibas Wirfneeki/\nun Mohsus runnaja us teem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 33,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Pehz to peegahje wiſſi\nIsraëta Behrni/ un winſch pa-\nwehleja teem wiſſu / ko tas\nKUNGS ar winnu bij runnajs\nus to Kalnu Sinai.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 34,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad beidse Mohsus ar\nteem runnaht/ un winſch bij wee-\nnu Apfeggu us faru Waigu\nlizzis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 35,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tomehr kad Mohsus\npreefsch ta KUNGA nahze / ar\nwinnu runnaht/ tad nornehme\nwinſch to Apfeggu / teekans\nwinſch isgahje / un kad winſch\nbija isgahjis/ tad runnaja winſch\nus Israëta Behrneem/ kas win-\nnam bija pawehlehts.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 36,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad redfeja Israëta Behr-\nnt Mohsus Waigu/ ka ta Ahda\n3\nno\n"
    }
